Jane Gurnett https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jane_Gurnett 0 Jane E. Gurnett (born March 1957, Dorset) is an English actress best known for her leading roles in British TV series Casualty (from 1994 to 1996), Dangerfield (1998–1999) and the second incarnation of Crossroads (2001–2003). The actress moved to Warwick School to teach drama and has been there since 2010.
